    <div class="col-xs-12 debate-date">
        <strong>28 January 1947</strong>
    </div>

    <div class="col-xs-12 debate-date">Volume 432</div>

    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
        <div class="container">
            <div id="debateContent">
                <div class="highlightedSearchTerms"></div>
                <div class="content-container">


<div class="content-item other-content">
        <!-- START statement -->
        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-c8fd95e4-f30a-444d-994c-6aec3f3fe010'>
            
<p class=""><em>The following Questions stood upon the Order Paper;</em></p>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            </div>
        <div class="clearfix"></div>
        <!-- END statement -->
</div>

<div class="content-item other-content">
        <!-- START statement -->
        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-d7a8ebd9-f5b7-4c5e-bc07-f67cef1d1c7d'>
            
<p class="">119. Mr. LIPSON,—To ask the Secretary of State for War if he is now able to say that, henceforth, marriage allowances will be paid to soldiers under 21.</p>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            </div>
        <div class="clearfix"></div>
        <!-- END statement -->
</div>

<div class="content-item other-content">
        <!-- START statement -->
        <div class="statement col-md-9 hs_ColumnNumber content-container " >
                <span data-toggle="tooltip" data-hop-debug-tooltip class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign hidden hidden-xs" data-placement="bottom" title=" hs_ColumnNumber "></span>

<p class="hs_ColumnNumber"><span id="771" class="column-number column-only" data-column-number="771"></span></p>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            </div>
        <div class="clearfix"></div>
        <!-- END statement -->
</div>

<div class="content-item other-content">
        <!-- START statement -->
        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-f5f65434-5802-49f5-96cf-62b266b4ddad'>
            
<p class="">123. Mr. GEORGE WALLACE,—To ask the Secretary of State for War if he will make a statement on the payment of marriage allowances to soldiers under 21 years of age.</p>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            </div>
        <div class="clearfix"></div>
        <!-- END statement -->
</div>

<div class="content-item other-content">
        <!-- START statement -->
        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-3e4f60e5-61e2-4943-961f-2d1ef47d2f55'>
            
<p class="">124. Mr. CHETWYND,—To ask the Secretary of State for War if he is now in a position to agree to the payment of marriage allowances to soldiers under 21 years of age, including members of the Regular Army.</p>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            </div>
        <div class="clearfix"></div>
        <!-- END statement -->
</div>

<div class="content-item other-content">
        <!-- START statement -->
        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-97f78781-96b0-4889-83c4-428196355c8e'>
            
<p class=""><em>At the end of Questions</em>—</p>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            </div>
        <div class="clearfix"></div>
        <!-- END statement -->
</div><div class="content-item" id="contribution-3ed93036-e482-4882-b3d7-fa5e2a3d06ea">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-3ed93036-e482-4882-b3d7-fa5e2a3d06ea">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-3ed93036-e482-4882-b3d7-fa5e2a3d06ea">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-3ed93036-e482-4882-b3d7-fa5e2a3d06ea">
                Mr. Bellenger
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-3ed93036-e482-4882-b3d7-fa5e2a3d06ea" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1947-01-28/debates/550c916d-2d6e-4c9a-b1c6-65c6efdcaba0/ServicesMarriageAllowance(MenUnder21)#contribution-3ed93036-e482-4882-b3d7-fa5e2a3d06ea">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">With the permission of the House, I will answer Questions Nos. 119, 123 and 124.<p></p> It has been decided that married soldiers under 21 years of age shall be eligible for marriage allowance at the same rates and under the same conditions as men over that age, but that they will not be entitled to any other married benefits such as provision of quarters or passages to overseas stations. The decision will apply equally to the Royal Navy and the Royal Air Force, and will take effect from 1st February, 1947. Payment will begin as soon as the necessary arrangements can be made. The question of the application of this arrangement to men called up for compulsory service from 1st January, 1949, is under consideration.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-3ed93036-e482-4882-b3d7-fa5e2a3d06ea" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1947-01-28/debates/550c916d-2d6e-4c9a-b1c6-65c6efdcaba0/ServicesMarriageAllowance(MenUnder21)#contribution-3ed93036-e482-4882-b3d7-fa5e2a3d06ea">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-af6c10ed-a21c-45fa-90fc-d32d9558fa10">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-af6c10ed-a21c-45fa-90fc-d32d9558fa10">
