        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-af6c10ed-a21c-45fa-90fc-d32d9558fa10">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-af6c10ed-a21c-45fa-90fc-d32d9558fa10">
                Mr. Lipson
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-af6c10ed-a21c-45fa-90fc-d32d9558fa10" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1947-01-28/debates/550c916d-2d6e-4c9a-b1c6-65c6efdcaba0/ServicesMarriageAllowance(MenUnder21)#contribution-af6c10ed-a21c-45fa-90fc-d32d9558fa10">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">While thanking the Minister for the concession which he has announced, may I ask him whether his answer means that payment will be made retrospective, in view of the fact that the families of some of these men have had to incur debts?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-af6c10ed-a21c-45fa-90fc-d32d9558fa10" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1947-01-28/debates/550c916d-2d6e-4c9a-b1c6-65c6efdcaba0/ServicesMarriageAllowance(MenUnder21)#contribution-af6c10ed-a21c-45fa-90fc-d32d9558fa10">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-e14788fb-88f6-4717-b9fd-8501e21d662e">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-e14788fb-88f6-4717-b9fd-8501e21d662e">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-e14788fb-88f6-4717-b9fd-8501e21d662e">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-e14788fb-88f6-4717-b9fd-8501e21d662e">
                Mr. Bellenger
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-e14788fb-88f6-4717-b9fd-8501e21d662e" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1947-01-28/debates/550c916d-2d6e-4c9a-b1c6-65c6efdcaba0/ServicesMarriageAllowance(MenUnder21)#contribution-e14788fb-88f6-4717-b9fd-8501e21d662e">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">No, Sir. I said that payments would start from 1st February, 1947. I think I should dispose of the point which has been put by the hon. Member, and by other Members, on more than one occasion. So far as my information goes, there has been no wide incurring of debt by these soldiers.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-e14788fb-88f6-4717-b9fd-8501e21d662e" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1947-01-28/debates/550c916d-2d6e-4c9a-b1c6-65c6efdcaba0/ServicesMarriageAllowance(MenUnder21)#contribution-e14788fb-88f6-4717-b9fd-8501e21d662e">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-5abb0b5e-5f0a-4c59-8512-72f29b9b834a">
